{"tid":2012934,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國際期刊撤下大批造假華論文","createTime":"2020-05-12T03:49:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T03:52:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"508aad663e227d360a723c074b8ded0b8afc70b8","tid":2012934,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:49:35.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200512/WTBNABSVJPM7WIGBK4EJTO4UIA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200512%2FWTBNABSVJPM7WIGBK4EJTO4UIA%2F&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97HdTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=966498e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200512%2FWTBNABSVJPM7WIGBK4EJTO4UIA%2F&h=06cf2577\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200512/WTBNABSVJPM7WIGBK4EJTO4UIA/</a><br />\n<br />\n國際期刊撤下大批造假華論文<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200512/large/1589214399_4036.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200512%2Flarge%2F1589214399_4036.jpg&h=a1866bef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國論文再被揭造假醜聞；圖為涉事學府之一浙江大學。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n中國學術論文再被揭造假。今年4月，國際著名學術出版集團施普林格（Springer Group）旗下期刊《多媒體工具與應用》，撤銷了33篇論文，加上該期刊近兩年撤下的另八篇論文，總共有41篇論文被撤，其中39篇論文的主要作者來自中國。事件在中國學術圈掀起一次規模不小「地震」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩年撤39篇<br />\n<br />\n據內媒報道，該39篇來自中國的論文被撤銷，撤稿理由包括剽竊他人未。。。。。。。。。<br />\n。<br />\n人尷尬的是，部份論文還獲得中國政府的項目資助。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，這已非中國學術圈在國際刊物首次集體出醜。2017年4月，施普林格集團旗下的《腫瘤生物學》雜誌一次過撤。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n向，但因學界觀念不改，在國際期刊發論文仍是晉升、爭科研項目、基金資助等的評定標準，故造假風氣難改。<br />\n<br />\n《光明日報》"},{"pid":"768002fcc1e6d3400869ded6adc6961ac7f8816e","tid":2012934,"uid":31200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:50:43.000Z","msg":"This is china.jpg"},{"pid":"704ab644c5b2521a5e35da272681b317ae2e9b43","tid":2012934,"uid":288707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T03:52:21.000Z","msg":"支那關華咩事"}]}